      "writtenOn": "2026-05-07T11:42:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Why is this a property and not an argument?  I see it is read-only... but that implies that a device can only support a single reset type.  That is surprising.",
      "revId": "379ab5afb8ba0de7286dd93cc5afb5c0e22ea3bd",
